    <h4>
      <a id="user-content-code-2" class="anchor" href="#code-2" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="octicon octicon-link"></span>
      </a>
      <code>code</code>
    </h4>

    <pre><code>    ```python
import random

class CardGame(object):
    """ a sample python class """
    NB_CARDS = 32
    def __init__(self, cards=5):
        self.cards = random.sample(range(self.NB_CARDS), 5)
        print 'ready to play'
        ```
</code></pre>

    <h4>
      <a id="user-content-效果-2" class="anchor" href="#%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C-2" aria-hidden="true">
